<br>
Monks - Plane of Air<br>
Warrior - Plane of Hate &amp; Plane of Air<br>
Magician - Plane of Hate &amp; Plane of Air<br>
Rogue - Plane of Hate<br>
Wizard - Plane of Fear<br>
Enchanter - Plane of Air &amp; Plane of Fear<br>
Necromancer - Plane of Hate, Plane of Air<br>
<br>
That just lists a few. I might have missed some and yes I know I didn't list all the classes. However if Verant made Ragefire spawn every 24 hours and put it on like the 4th island on the plane of air, then there wouldn't be as much bickering on the last part of their epic.<br>
